description: Document Search provides with basic details of documents that have been lodged with ASIC and allows to order copies of them
name: Document Search by ABN or ACN

elements.name: AS-DSA-001 Search a document by document numbers

steps.name: the user logs in with valid credentials on web application
the user navigates to asic search
the user is on Document Search by ABN or ACN search tab
the user provides client matter reference number
the user enters the ACN or ABN details
the user select the period - "All"
the user searches for the organisation
selects the relevant document
places an order for the document
the user visualizes the organisation extract summary report

description: Document Search provides with basic details of documents that have been lodged with ASIC and allows to order copies of them

elements.name: AS-DS-001 Notify user to verify documents before placing an order

steps.name: the user logs in with valid credentials on web application
the user navigates to asic search
the user is on Document search tab
the user enters document number
the user enters matter reference number
the user submits the order for documents
user visualizes an error message to verify documents before order - "You must select at least one verified document to order"

description:
A Personal Name extract will contain the person's name, birth details, organisation name, ABN/ACN
        number and current status, role(s) held by the person and residential address as well as the date
        appointed, and date ceased, and where applicable: banned futures representatives, banned securities
        representative and disqualified directors.
name: Personal Name

elements.name: AS-PN-001 Search Personal Extract based on Extract Type Current

steps.name: the user logs in with valid credentials on web application
the user navigates to asic search
the user is on Personal Name search tab
the user provides matter reference for personal name search
the user provides personal name and date of birth
the user selects Personal Extract Type - "Current"
the user looks up for the relevant person
the user selects the required personal information
the user places an order for the personal name extract
the user visualizes the organisation extract summary report

description:
ASIC's professional registers provide information about professionals, including liquidators, auditors and
    licensees. A professional register extract will include information on an individual such as their current
    place of practice, companies in which they have a recorded role, company address and the dates of
    appointment and cessation.
name: Professional Search

elements.name: AS-PS-001 - Search ASIC for professional registers Smith

steps.name: the user logs in with valid credentials on web application
the user navigates to asic search
the user is on Professional Search tab
the user provides professional matter reference
